---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Tentang Saya — Muhammad Nurhidayat Gani">
  <Header />
  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-gray-50">Tentang Saya</h1>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-start mb-20">
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <div class="aspect-square rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-dark-800 border border-gray-600/30">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" 
            alt="Potret profesional Muhammad Nurhidayat Gani" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover" 
            loading="lazy"
            width="800"
            height="800"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6 text-gray-400">
        <div class="space-y-5 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-50">
            From operating excavators to engineering digital solutions — precision matters in both worlds.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg">
            Saya Muhammad Nurhidayat Gani, seorang profesional yang memulai karier sebagai <span class="text-primary-400 font-semibold">Heavy Equipment Operator</span> dengan spesialisasi excavator di operasi penambangan nikel. Selama bertahun-tahun di lapangan, saya membangun fondasi kuat dalam hal presisi operasional, keselamatan kerja (K3), dan efisiensi sistem.
          </p>

          <p>
            Di dunia pertambangan, saya mencapai <span class="text-primary-400 font-semibold">95% efisiensi operasional</span> dengan produksi konsisten 800-1,000 BCM per hari. Saya juga menurunkan insiden near-miss hingga <span class="text-primary-400 font-semibold">40%</span> melalui implementasi protokol keselamatan yang ketat, dan mempertahankan <span class="text-primary-400 font-semibold">96% uptime</span> pada equipment melalui perawatan preventif yang disiplin.
          </p>

          <p>
            Kini saya bertransisi ke <span class="text-primary-400 font-semibold">software development</span>, membawa prinsip yang sama: struktur yang solid, testing yang komprehensif, dan monitoring yang ketat. Saya fokus membangun aplikasi production-ready dengan pendekatan yang sama cermatnya seperti mengoperasikan excavator — setiap movement harus calculated, setiap decision harus data-driven.
          </p>

          <p>
            Spesialisasi saya ada pada <span class="text-primary-400 font-semibold">backend systems</span> dan <span class="text-primary-400 font-semibold">automation</span>. Saya membangun WhatsApp e-commerce bot yang menangani 100+ customer per hari dengan <span class="text-primary-400 font-semibold">99% uptime</span>, mengintegrasikan AI untuk natural language processing, dan mengoptimalkan sistem untuk berjalan di VPS dengan resource minimal — sama seperti memaksimalkan produktivitas equipment dengan resource terbatas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-600/30">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4 text-gray-50">Career Highlights</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary-400 mt-1">▸</span>
              <span><strong class="text-gray-300">Heavy Equipment Operations:</strong> 95% efficiency, 800-1,000 BCM daily production</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary-400 mt-1">▸</span>
              <span><strong class="text-gray-300">Safety Leadership:</strong> 40% reduction in near-miss incidents, Safety Champion Award</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary-400 mt-1">▸</span>
              <span><strong class="text-gray-300">Equipment Excellence:</strong> 96% uptime achievement, Rp 85M+ annual cost savings</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary-400 mt-1">▸</span>
              <span><strong class="text-gray-300">Software Development:</strong> Built production systems with 99% uptime and 99.7% test coverage</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-50">Tech Stack & Skills</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="dark-card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-50 text-lg">Frontend Development</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['React 18','Next.js 14','Astro','TypeScript','Tailwind CSS','Framer Motion'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs rounded-md bg-dark-700 text-gray-300 border border-gray-600/30">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="dark-card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-50 text-lg">Backend & APIs</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['Node.js 20','Express','REST API','WhatsApp API','Webhook Systems','Cron Jobs'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs rounded-md bg-dark-700 text-gray-300 border border-gray-600/30">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="dark-card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-50 text-lg">AI & Automation</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['Google Gemini','Vercel AI SDK','NLP','Intent Classification','Prompt Engineering'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs rounded-md bg-dark-700 text-gray-300 border border-gray-600/30">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="dark-card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-50 text-lg">Database & Storage</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['Redis','PostgreSQL','File-based Systems','Session Management'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs rounded-md bg-dark-700 text-gray-300 border border-gray-600/30">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="dark-card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-50 text-lg">Testing & Quality</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['Jest','Supertest','Unit Testing','Integration Tests','CI/CD','ESLint'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs rounded-md bg-dark-700 text-gray-300 border border-gray-600/30">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="dark-card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-50 text-lg">DevOps & Deployment</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['Git','GitHub Actions','PM2','VPS Management','Vercel','CDN'].map(t => 
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs rounded-md bg-dark-700 text-gray-300 border border-gray-600/30">{t}</span>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-8 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="dark-card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-50">Core Principles</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-gray-400">
            <li>• Modular architecture dengan single responsibility</li>
            <li>• Test-driven development (80%+ coverage)</li>
            <li>• Performance optimization untuk low-resource environments</li>
            <li>• Security-first approach (input validation, XSS prevention)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="dark-card p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-50">Currently Learning</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-gray-400">
            <li>• Advanced AI prompt engineering techniques</li>
            <li>• Microservices architecture patterns</li>
            <li>• Real-time data streaming (WebSockets)</li>
            <li>• Cloud-native development (AWS/GCP)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
      <a href="/resume.html" target="_blank" class="cta-button inline-block">
        View Resume (PDF)
      </a>
      <a href="/resume-content.md" download class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-gray-600 text-gray-300 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:border-primary-500 hover:text-primary-400 transition-all">
        Download Markdown
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
